snippet.title: Christmas Celebration With Sakuya Izayoi - Full Gameplay / (PC)
snippet.description: Celebrate Christmas with Sakuya Izayoi from the Touhou Project in this cozy visual novel! Explore the colourful sights of the human village in Gensokyo as it hosts a one of a kind festival with several venues and gorgeous sights to see!
